For our anxious bathers, we have Perfect Calm Shampoo which has wonderful aromatherapy qualities of lavender and chamomile that help soothe and relax while it cleans.

[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=”1_4″ _builder_version=”4.22.1″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_blurb title=”Simple Shed Treatment” image=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/003-shampoo-1-300×300.png” icon_placement=”left” image_icon_width=”36px” icon_placement_tablet=”left” icon_placement_phone=”top” icon_placement_last_edited=”on|phone” _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” background_layout=”dark” text_orientation_tablet=”” text_orientation_phone=”center” text_orientation_last_edited=”on|phone” global_colors_info=”{}” custom_margin_last_edited=”on|phone” custom_margin_phone=”||50px||false|false” hover_enabled=”0″ sticky_enabled=”0″]

For our heavy shedders, we have Simple Shed Shampoo/Treatment. It’s specially formulated to release loose hair and undercoat while it cleans.

[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=”1_4″ _builder_version=”4.22.1″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_blurb title=”Bright White Shampoo” image=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/003-shampoo-1-300×300.png” icon_placement=”left” image_icon_width=”36px” icon_placement_tablet=”left” icon_placement_phone=”top” icon_placement_last_edited=”on|phone” _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” background_layout=”dark” hover_enabled=”0″ text_orientation_tablet=”” text_orientation_phone=”center” text_orientation_last_edited=”on|phone” global_colors_info=”{}” custom_margin_last_edited=”on|phone” custom_margin_phone=”||50px||false|false” sticky_enabled=”0″]

Bright White Shampoo is formulated with an optical brightener to restore brilliance to white and light-colored fur, leaving behind a fresh, shiny coat. Improves and enhances color and contrast in coats.

[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=”1_4″ _builder_version=”4.22.1″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_blurb title=”Oatmeal Baking Soda Shampoo” image=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/003-shampoo-1-300×300.png” icon_placement=”left” image_icon_width=”36px” icon_placement_tablet=”left” icon_placement_phone=”top” icon_placement_last_edited=”on|phone” _builder_version=”4.22.1″ _module_preset=”default” background_layout=”dark” text_orientation_tablet=”” text_orientation_phone=”center” text_orientation_last_edited=”on|phone” global_colors_info=”{}”]

Oatmeal Baking Soda Shampoo combines oatmeal (a natural soothing agent), baking soda (an odor neutralizer), and aloe vera (a coat and skin hydrator), for a fresh and soothing bath. Reduces odors and calms itchy irritations.

[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=”1_4,1_4,1_4,1_4″ use_custom_gutter=”on” _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” max_width=”1280px” custom_margin=”35px|auto||auto|false|false” custom_margin_tablet=”35px|auto||auto|false|false” custom_margin_phone=”0px||||false|false” custom_margin_last_edited=”on|phone” custom_padding=”||24px|||” hover_enabled=”0″ global_colors_info=”{}” sticky_enabled=”0″][et_pb_column type=”1_4″ _builder_version=”4.22.1″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_blurb title=”Flea & Tick Shampoo” image=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/003-shampoo-1-300×300.png” icon_placement=”left” image_icon_width=”36px” icon_placement_tablet=”left” icon_placement_phone=”top” icon_placement_last_edited=”on|phone” _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” background_layout=”dark” hover_enabled=”0″ text_orientation_tablet=”” text_orientation_phone=”center” text_orientation_last_edited=”on|phone” global_colors_info=”{}” custom_margin=”||||false|false” sticky_enabled=”0″ custom_margin_last_edited=”on|phone” custom_margin_phone=”50px||50px||false|false” custom_margin_tablet=”||||false|false”]

We also carry a Flea and Tick Shampoo that kills fleas and ticks on dogs and puppies (more than 12 weeks old), cleans and conditions pets’ coats, and leaves pets smelling fresh and clean.

[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=”1_4″ _builder_version=”4.22.1″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_blurb title=”Remoisturizer Conditioner” image=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/003-shampoo-1-300×300.png” icon_placement=”left” image_icon_width=”36px” icon_placement_tablet=”left” icon_placement_phone=”top” icon_placement_last_edited=”on|phone” _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” background_layout=”dark” hover_enabled=”0″ text_orientation_tablet=”” text_orientation_phone=”center” text_orientation_last_edited=”on|phone” global_colors_info=”{}” custom_margin=”||50px||false|false” sticky_enabled=”0″]

Luxury Remoisturizer Conditioner is an easy-to-use hair revitalizing formula. Organic aloe vera and effective conditioners penetrate the hair shaft and rehydrate the skin and coat.

[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=”1_4″ _builder_version=”4.22.1″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_blurb title=”Plum Perfect Facial Cleanser” image=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/003-shampoo-1-300×300.png” icon_placement=”left” image_icon_width=”36px” icon_placement_tablet=”left” icon_placement_phone=”top” icon_placement_last_edited=”on|phone” _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” background_layout=”dark” hover_enabled=”0″ text_orientation_tablet=”” text_orientation_phone=”center” text_orientation_last_edited=”on|phone” global_colors_info=”{}” custom_margin=”||50px||false|false” sticky_enabled=”0″]

On faces, we use Plum Perfect Facial Cleanser. This gentle foaming facial cleanser removes dirt and unsightly tear and food stains while brightening any facial coloring.

My dog has enjoyed daycare & boarding at Underdog! The staff is great, from the curbside check-in & check-out to multiple photos throughout the day. We have no issues/concerns when we drop our dog off. Highly recommend.

[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=”1_3″ _builder_version=”4.21.2″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_testimonial author=”Megan Lee” job_title=” ★★★★★” portrait_url=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-12-at-10.41.03 AM.png” quote_icon_color=”#977740″ quote_icon_background_color=”RGBA(255,255,255,0)” font_icon=”||divi||400″ _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” author_text_color=”#977740″ background_color=”rgba(239,232,220,0.61)” custom_css_free_form=”.et_pb_testimonial_description::after {|| diplay: block !important;|| content: url(https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/7123025_logo_google_g_icon-4-e1702060453451.png);|| margin-left: -2px !important;|| ||}” box_shadow_style=”preset3″ global_colors_info=”{}”]

It was Poppy’s first time going to day care and they were so good about asking about her play-style, temperament, and friend size preferences. She’s a middle aged girly who enjoys little dogs a lot, so she got to play with the smalls, which isn’t always the case at daycares. I got pictures of her sent to me, along with an update on her day, which is so nice for a pet parent.
She came home happy and relaxed- We will be coming back! Thank y’all!!

[/et_pb_testimonial][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=”1_3″ _builder_version=”4.21.2″ _module_preset=”default” global_colors_info=”{}”][et_pb_testimonial author=”Rebecca Barr” job_title=” ★★★★★” portrait_url=”https://underdog-kennels.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Screenshot-2024-07-12-at-10.43.12 AM.png” quote_icon_color=”#977740″ quote_icon_background_color=”RGBA(255,255,255,0)” font_icon=”||divi||400″ _builder_version=”4.25.1″ _module_preset=”default” author_text_color=”#977740″ background_color=”rgba(239,232,220,0.61)” box_shadow_style=”preset3″ global_colors_info=”{}”]

I have a 7lb anxious mini doxin and underdog not only took her in (finding a GOOD place that will take an under 10lb-er was hard) but makes her feel comfortable, gives her extra human attention when she freaks, and has turf (not concrete) for the Texas outdoor sun. Can’t recommend enough
